Extension Features:

1. Automatically shuffle One Piece Chibi wallpapers each time you open a new tab.
2. Choose a random One Piece Chibi background or set a favorite in the wallpaper selection panel.
3. Integrated Google search bar.
4. Convenient links to your email and social media profiles.
5. Automatically display the current date and time.
6. Create new notes to track your tasks.
7. Quick links to your frequently visited sites.
8. Simplified access to your bookmarks.
9. Shortcut panel for adding and accessing favorite websites quickly.
10. Direct links to Google applications.
11. Quick links to additional themes.
12. Simplified social media sharing.
13. Easy download options for wallpapers.
14. Instant access to gaming.
